---
title: Hearty Mushroom & Veggie Casserole with Garlic Rice & Parsley
description: This hearty meal is proof that veggie-based meals don’t need to sacrifice on big flavours! Mushrooms are cooked down in a rich and creamy tomato-based casserole that warms you up to your bones. Paired with fragrant and fluffy garlic rice, this dish is a sure-fire winner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/667def98004ad21ab42e46df-0a2dece5.jpeg
